## PROHIBITED Alpha Behaviors

❌ **Sheep Behavior:** Chasing green candles, panic selling red candles
❌ **Revenge Trading:** Re-entering immediately after stop-loss
❌ **Hope Trading:** Holding losers hoping they recover
❌ **Greed Trading:** Not taking profit, wanting more
❌ **Boredom Trading:** Trading for action, not opportunity
❌ **Ego Trading:** Refusing to admit being wrong
❌ **Herd Fighting:** Shorting parabolic moves, buying crashes

---

## Code Review Checklist

Before approving any strategy code:

- [ ] Does it STALK (wait for confirmation) or CHASE (react immediately)?
- [ ] Does it know its TERRAIN (regime-aware)?
- [ ] Does it CONSERVE energy (quality over quantity)?
- [ ] Does it SENSE shifts (leading indicators)?
- [ ] Does it DISENGAGE fast (proper stop-loss)?
- [ ] Does it RESPECT the herd (trend filter)?
- [ ] Does it SIZE appropriately (risk-adjusted)?
- [ ] Does it REST (cooldown periods)?
- [ ] Does it have MULTIPLE EXITS (stop, target, time)?
- [ ] Does it REMEMBER (logging, attribution)?

